Language: <F P=105> Greek </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A bomb exploded near Faneromeni Church in Nicosia at 
approximately 2300 yesterday, causing no casualties or damage 
[as heard]. The explosion occurred outside the mosque on 
Lefkonos Street behind Faneromeni Church. The explosion 
shattered windows of shops nearby. Police have cordoned off the 
area and investigations will continue today to establish the 
cause of the blast. The police are also investigating the 
possibility that the explosion is a provocation by the Turks. 

